flowchart LR
    A[Source File] --> B{Detect Type}
    B -->|.mermaid .mmd| C[Mermaid]
    B -->|.excalidraw| D[Excalidraw]
    B -->|.drawio .dio| E[Draw.io]
    B -->|.dot .gv| F[Graphviz]
    C --> G[Browser Pool<br/>Chromium]
    D --> G
    E --> G
    F --> H[Viz.js WASM]
    G --> I[SVG Output]
    H --> I
    I --> J{Raster?}
    J -->|No| K[Write SVG]
    J -->|Yes| L[sharp]
    L --> M[PNG / JPEG /<br/>WebP / AVIF]
    K --> N[Atomic Write<br/>.tmp → rename]
    M --> N
